citation.case_name: Andrade, AKA Guerraro-Perez v. United States

html:
543 U.S. 1105

ANDRADE, AKA GUERRARO-PEREZ
v.
UNITED STATES.

No. 04-5716.

Supreme Court of United States.

January 24, 2005.

1

C. A. 5th Cir. Reported below: 96 Fed. Appx. 241; Motions of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted, judgments vacated, and cases remanded for further consideration in light of United States v. Booker, ante, p. 220.
